Functions

Class Function

  • java.lang.Object
    • Functions.Function
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Add, Literal, Power, Round, Subtract

    public abstract class Function
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class for function. Functions should override some methods. The Function class defines a static Parse method to convert Strings to Functions
    Author:
    Jan-Willem Gmelig Meyling
